  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink36-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">tāṉ vāyiṉēruṅ kuṟippiṉaḷāṉamai aṟiyātu tōḻi vāyil maṟuttuḻi avaḷ nērum
          vakaiyāl avaṭkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink36">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi yūra</l>
          <l> ṉammaṟan tamaikuva ṉāyi ṉāmaṟan</l>
          <l> tuḷḷā tamaitalu mamaikuva maṉṉē</l>
          <l> kayaleṉak karutiya vuṇkaṇ</l>
          <l> pacalaik kolkā vākutal peṟiṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> Alas, [my] friend!</l>
          <l> If the man from the village is happy to forget us,</l>
          <l> my carp-like black kajal-eyes</l> 
          <l> will be quite happy </l>
          <l> to not think of him, to forget him–</l>
          <l> unless they grow weak from pallor.</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
